        "text": "Not at all. The three landscapes of the foprop frame turn out to be three distinct **modes of materiality**, all of which are inescapably present in practice - in an activist *life*, in the *formation* of an activist life and an activist capability - and are utterly material to liberation, formaciòn, provisioning, the remaking of the mode of production: the survival and the leaving, in deep time and not before time, of the anthropocene, the colonial-capitalist commodity-enclosed economy, and the new-born, deeply risky, golemic. \n"
